Class QueryConverterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • retrofit2.Converter.Factory
      • io.github.iwyfewwnt.uwretrofit.converters.QueryConverterFactory

  • public final class QueryConverterFactory
extends retrofit2.Converter.Factory
    A query converter factory.

    Can be used to convert custom query parameters to string. Extends from Converter.Factory.
